RockyLinux is a light weight RHEL version. It can be setup locally over virtual box.

Install VirtualBox 6.x 
Install vagrant

MACOS:
------

>> brew install vagrant --cask

>> mkdir vagrant/rockylinux
>> cd vagrant/rockylinux

>> vagrant init generic/rocky8
>> vagrant up
>> vagrant ssh

incase vm got some issue:
>> vagrant global-status
this will list the vm id.

>> vagrant destroy <vm id>
